  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">STAR 2 - Facilitating CSOs engagement with Government</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Development and strengthening of a culture within government, of listening and engaging with CSOs in the fight against corruption.
2. De-politicisation of corruption issues.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Formation of a project steering committee
2. Hold initial discourse with national level CSOs on project concept, their role and outline specific of good governance and anti-corruption intervention areas for engagement
3. Conduct one national and five (5) regional level CSO dialogues on relevant issues of good governance and anti-corruption
4. Conduct national CSO engagement forums with the three arms of government 
5. Conduct CSO lesson-learning and feedback  forum after each national CSO-government forum  and Disseminate of issues emerging from CSO-government engagement:</narrative>
  </description>
